keyMappings:
unmap t
unmap T
unmap gi
unmap gt
unmap gT
unmap x
unmap X
unmap J
unmap K
unmap ^

map h goBack
map l goForward
map i focusInput
map I enterInsertMode
map qq removeTab
map Q restoreTab
map R reload hard
map t Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map <C-j> previousTab
map <C-k> nextTab
map <C-o> visitPreviousTab
map . noop
